            <script type="text/javascript">
             function bindEvents() {
        $(".gallery-close-container").unbind('click');
        $(".gallery-close-container").click(function () {
            $(".gallery-container").fadeOut();
            $(".gallery-overlay").hide();
        });

        $(".thumbnail-image-container").unbind('hover');
        $(".thumbnail-image-container").hover(function () {
            $("#ctl00_MainContentPlaceHolder_productImage1").attr('src', $(this).find('img').attr('src'));
            $(".thumbnail-image-container").removeClass("currentImage");
            $(this).addClass('currentImage');
        }, function () { });

        $(".thumbnail-image-container").unbind('click');
        $(".thumbnail-image-container").click(function () {
            displayGallery();
        });

        if ($(".thumbnail-image-container").length &gt; 0) {
            $("#ctl00_MainContentPlaceHolder_productImage1").unbind('click');
            $("#ctl00_MainContentPlaceHolder_productImage1").click(function() {
                displayGallery();
            });
        }
        
        $(".gallery-slider").anythingSlider({
            easing: "easeInOutExpo",
            autoPlay: true,
            startStopped: true,
            animationTime: 500,
            hashTags: false,
            buildNavigation: false,
            pauseOnHover: true
        });

        $(".thumbnail-image-container:first").addClass("currentImage");
        $(".gallery-slider").anythingSlider(1);
        $(".gallery-container").attr('style', 'width:600px;height:600px;display:none;');

        setTimeout(function() {
            $(".gallery-overlay").height($(document).height());
        }, 1500);
    }

    function displayGallery() {
        $(".thumbnail-image-container").each(function (i, v) {
            if ($(v).hasClass('currentImage')) {
                $(".gallery-slider").anythingSlider(i + 1);
                return false;
            }
        });

        setTimeout(function () {
            $(".gallery-container").fadeIn();
            $(".gallery-overlay").show();
        }, 500);
    }

    bindEvents();
            </script>
